      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the chicken is cooking, chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>remaining garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the<strong> chopped parsley</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and<strong> half</strong> your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) in a bowl with the <strong>warmed butter </strong>and a generous pinch of<strong> salt </strong>– this is your <strong>cheesy garlic butter</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1679579983747-x200.jpg",
