            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble your burger, top the <strong>garlic bread base </strong>with the <strong>pulled chicken</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>roasted garlic aioli</strong> and a<strong> lettuce leaf</strong>, then finish with the <strong>garlic bread lid</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>lettuce quarters</strong> with a drizzle of <strong>roasted garlic aioli</strong> and sprinkle over the <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>smoky chips</strong> and any <strong>remaining aioli</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
